<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٥٤٤ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5178">قَبِيصَةُ بْنُ عُقْبَةَ </a>: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">سُفْيَانُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3037">عَاصِمٍ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3071">الشَّعْبِيِّ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3732">ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«آخِرُ آيَةٍ نَزَلَتْ عَلَى النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> آيَةُ الرِّبَا.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>